Package data_representation

Class StateSequence

java.lang.Object
data_representation.StateSequence
All Implemented Interfaces:
HelpTarget, DataRepresentation, java.io.Serializable, java.util.Iterator<java.lang.Object>
public class StateSequence
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataRepresentation
this is a data representation for a format used in the case studies. This format starts with an id enclosed in square brackets, and then is a dash-separated list of states then events: [] State---... this particular data representation reads that format in, but only stores the states in the list
